
<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">Road safety</h1>

<section class="govuk-section datagovuk-section">
    <p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">Data for road collisions in England, Scotland and Wales from 1979, and the vehicles and casualties involved. The statistics relate to personal injury collisions on public roads that are reported to the police. The data is published annually and contains all the non-sensitive fields that can be made public.</p>
</section>


